{
  "project_id": "mastodon-status-fanout",
  "_note": "Reconstructed Mastodon pilot input (the original run-008 artifacts were never persisted; the SDK's mastodon o11y tests use inline synthetic _meta). Faithful to the pilot structure: the phantom 'mastodon' umbrella stem (#241, filtered), two traces-only services (#274 base-SLI suppression), and one metrics-emitting service whose SLI carries the real OTel service.name with a slash (#275). Consumed by generate_observability_artifacts(); replayed by 'startd8 observability compare-live'.",
